sequenceDiagram
    participant "RabbitMQ Broker" as RabbitMQBroker
    participant "AI Processing Worker" as AIProcessingWorker
    participant "PostgreSQL Database" as PostgreSQLDatabase
    participant "AWS S3" as AWSS3
    participant "AWS Comprehend API" as AWSComprehendAPI
    participant "OpenAI API" as OpenAIAPI

    activate AIProcessingWorker
    RabbitMQBroker->>AIProcessingWorker: 1. Deliver 'SowUploaded' message
    AIProcessingWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabase: 2. Check SOW processing status for idempotency
    PostgreSQLDatabase-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return SOW status ('Pending', 'Processing', etc.)
    AIProcessingWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabase: 3. Update SOW status to 'Processing'
    PostgreSQLDatabase-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return rows affected
    AIProcessingWorker->>AWSS3: 4. Download original SOW document
    AWSS3-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return SOW document stream (e.g., .docx, .pdf)
    AIProcessingWorker->>AWSComprehendAPI: 5. Request PII entity detection
    AWSComprehendAPI-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return collection of detected PII entities and their locations
    AIProcessingWorker->>AWSS3: 6. Upload sanitized SOW text
    AWSS3-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return ETag of uploaded object
    AIProcessingWorker->>OpenAIAPI: 7. Request structured data extraction from sanitized text
    OpenAIAPI-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return structured JSON object
    AIProcessingWorker->>OpenAIAPI: 7.1. Attempt 1: POST /v1/chat/completions
    OpenAIAPI-->>AIProcessingWorker: 503 Service Unavailable
    AIProcessingWorker->>AIProcessingWorker: 7.2. Wait (Exponential Backoff + Jitter)
    AIProcessingWorker->>OpenAIAPI: 7.3. Attempt 2: POST /v1/chat/completions
    OpenAIAPI-->>AIProcessingWorker: 200 OK with JSON payload
    AIProcessingWorker->>OpenAIAPI: 8. Request vector embeddings for extracted skills
    OpenAIAPI-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return array of vector embeddings
    AIProcessingWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabase: 9. Persist extracted data, embeddings, and update status
    PostgreSQLDatabase-->>AIProcessingWorker: Return transaction commit success
    AIProcessingWorker->>RabbitMQBroker: 10. Acknowledge message processing complete

    note over AIProcessingWorker: If idempotency check at step 2 finds a status other than 'Pending', the worker logs a warning, AC...
    note over AIProcessingWorker: If any step fails after exhausting all retries (e.g., OpenAI API is down), the entire process is ...
    note over AIProcessingWorker: Upon successful completion at step 9, a 'SowProcessingCompleted' domain event is published intern...

    deactivate AIProcessingWorker
